data.description: Welcome to this charming single-family residence nestled in the sought-after community of Reed?s Crossing. Recently constructed in 2023, this home boasts modern amenities that surpass new builds, including a refrigerator, washer, dryer, and smart Ring security system. Sits on a quiet street, unlike current new construction options.The main floor welcomes you with an abundance of natural light and an open-concept layout, perfect for entertaining. Discover the heart of the home in the spacious great room, complemented by a generously sized kitchen island, ideal for culinary adventures and gathering with loved ones.Ascending to the second floor, you'll find a thoughtfully designed split layout offering privacy and comfort. The expansive primary suite is a peaceful retreat, featuring a luxurious walk-in closet, double sinks, and a rejuvenating walk-in shower. Convenience is key with a sizable laundry area conveniently located on the second level. Additional bedrooms on the second floor offer ample space and are bathed in natural light through plentiful windows, creating inviting spaces for relaxation and personalization.Come see it before it's gone.
